text: Has anyone had any trouble running graphql in a template?

I noticed you can now disable jQuery on a HubSpot site (Awesome!). What happens to modules that rely on jQuery? Does HubSpot automatically detect jQuery functions and add it or do we need to refactor the modules and/or add jQuery as a dependency?
I doubt that <@U7V9DQ31P> -- It just removes and your stuff will fail
The HubSpot developer chrome extension has an option on it to remove jquery from the page so you can preview it without taking it live on each page
